Information
------------------------------

The Coolest Places on Earth 
The Coolest Places on Earth takes viewers on a journey of discovery to the most astonishing places on the planet - cities, festivals, landmarks and jaw-dropping works of nature - exploring each location's history and culture, to discover why it deserves to be called one of the coolest places on earth!



8)  Florida Keys 
Today on the Coolest Places on Earth: We're on the road to happiness. If you're looking for an ocean of enjoyment and fun in the sun, we've got the keys...the Florida Keys, that is. Next, grab your parka. We're taking you to one of the happiest countries on the planet. And, from the awesome castles of the Scottish Highlands to the stunning beaches and waterfalls of Croatia, we're on a mission to escape the ordinary, and experience the extraordinary.
